folders.name: Commission API "/revenue/employee/(eid)"
folders.description: API to get commision for an employee

folders.name: Paycheck API: /paycheck/?:id
folders.description: API that returns the salary of some employee

folders.name: Verify Customer Support Employee: /verifyCustomerSupportEID/?:eid
folders.description: Returns true if the employee associated with the provided eid works in Customer Support, and false if not.

folders.name: Verify Employee: /getEmployeeDepartment/?:eID
folders.description: Returns the department a user is in, or returns that the eID does not exist or is invalid.

folders.name: Verify Sales Employee: /verifySalesEID/?:eid
folders.description: Returns true if the employee with associated eID is a Sales employee, and returns false otherwise.
